 s_n=\sum_{j=0}^n\left(-\frac12\right)^j 
 \begin{align} s_n+\frac12s_n &=\sum_{j=0}^n\left(-\frac12\right)^j-\sum_{j=1}^{n+1}\left(-\frac12\right)^j\\ &=1-\left(-\frac12\right)^{n+1} \end{align} 
